        High level capacity measurements for the entire cluster.
        Parameters:
        activeBlockSpace - [required] The amount of space on the block drives.
        activeSessions - [required] Number of active iSCSI sessions communicating with the cluster
        averageIOPS - [required] Average IPS for the cluster since midnight Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).
        clusterRecentIOSize - [required] The average size of IOPS to all volumes in the cluster.
        currentIOPS - [required] Average IOPS for all volumes in the cluster over the last 5 seconds.
        maxIOPS - [required] Estimated maximum IOPS capability of the current cluster.
        maxOverProvisionableSpace - [required] The maximum amount of provisionable space.
        maxProvisionedSpace - [required] The total amount of provisionable space if all volumes are 100% filled (no thin provisioned metadata).
        maxUsedMetadataSpace - [required] The amount of bytes on volume drives used to store metadata.
        maxUsedSpace - [required] The total amount of space on all active block drives.
        nonZeroBlocks - [required] Total number of 4KiB blocks with data after the last garbage collection operation has completed.
        peakActiveSessions - [required] Peak number of iSCSI connections since midnight UTC.
        peakIOPS - [required] The highest value for currentIOPS since midnight UTC.
        provisionedSpace - [required] Total amount of space provisioned in all volumes on the cluster.
        timestamp - [required] The date and time this cluster capacity sample was taken.
        totalOps - [required] The total number of I/O operations performed throughout the lifetime of the cluster
        uniqueBlocks - [required] The total number of blocks stored on the block drives.
        uniqueBlocksUsedSpace - [required] The total amount of data the uniqueBlocks take up on the block drives.
        usedMetadataSpace - [required] The total amount of bytes on volume drives used to store metadata
        usedMetadataSpaceInSnapshots - [required] The amount of bytes on volume drives used for storing unique data in snapshots.
        usedSpace - [required] Total amount of space used by all block drives in the system.
        zeroBlocks - [required] Total number of 4KiB blocks without data after the last round of garabage collection operation has completed.
        Since:
        7.0

        High level capacity measurements for the entire cluster.
        Parameters:
        activeBlockSpace - [required] The amount of space on the block drives.
        activeSessions - [required] Number of active iSCSI sessions communicating with the cluster
        averageIOPS - [required] Average IPS for the cluster since midnight Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).
        clusterRecentIOSize - [required] The average size of IOPS to all volumes in the cluster.
        currentIOPS - [required] Average IOPS for all volumes in the cluster over the last 5 seconds.
        maxIOPS - [required] Estimated maximum IOPS capability of the current cluster.
        maxOverProvisionableSpace - [required] The maximum amount of provisionable space.
        maxProvisionedSpace - [required] The total amount of provisionable space if all volumes are 100% filled (no thin provisioned metadata).
        maxUsedMetadataSpace - [required] The amount of bytes on volume drives used to store metadata.
        maxUsedSpace - [required] The total amount of space on all active block drives.
        nonZeroBlocks - [required] Total number of 4KiB blocks with data after the last garbage collection operation has completed.
        peakActiveSessions - [required] Peak number of iSCSI connections since midnight UTC.
        peakIOPS - [required] The highest value for currentIOPS since midnight UTC.
        provisionedSpace - [required] Total amount of space provisioned in all volumes on the cluster.
        snapshotNonZeroBlocks - [required] Total number of 4KiB blocks in snapshots with data.
        timestamp - [required] The date and time this cluster capacity sample was taken.
        totalOps - [required] The total number of I/O operations performed throughout the lifetime of the cluster
        uniqueBlocks - [required] The total number of blocks stored on the block drives.
        uniqueBlocksUsedSpace - [required] The total amount of data the uniqueBlocks take up on the block drives.
        usedMetadataSpace - [required] The total amount of bytes on volume drives used to store metadata
        usedMetadataSpaceInSnapshots - [required] The amount of bytes on volume drives used for storing unique data in snapshots.
        usedSpace - [required] Total amount of space used by all block drives in the system.
        zeroBlocks - [required] Total number of 4KiB blocks without data after the last round of garabage collection operation has completed.
        Since:
        8.0
